Some further wave parameter relations

ω   angular (temporal) frequency = 2πν = 2π/τ
V   velocity (meters/second) = νλ
ν   frequency 1/s or Hz (think of cycles/second)
λ   wavelength (meters)
k   propagation number = 2*π/λ (radians/meter)
